IRINA...WHY...

232
00:13:10,749 --> 00:13:12,250
COME.

233
00:13:17,464 --> 00:13:19,466
HOW COULD YOU
DO THIS TO YOURSELF?

234
00:13:19,591 --> 00:13:20,841
YOU WERE A SCIENTIST.

235
00:13:20,967 --> 00:13:22,427
AND NOW...LOOK AT YOU.

236
00:13:22,552 --> 00:13:24,845
LOOK AT YOURSELF,
PAVEL.

237
00:13:24,971 --> 00:13:26,847
WHY DID YOU DO IT?

238
00:13:26,973 --> 00:13:28,683
WHY DID YOU?

239
00:13:31,352 --> 00:13:34,147
I AM PROUD
OF WHAT I AM.

240
00:13:34,272 --> 00:13:36,023
I BELIEVE IN WHAT I DO.

241
00:13:36,149 --> 00:13:37,734
CAN YOU SAY THAT?

242
00:13:37,858 --> 00:13:38,652
YES.

243
00:13:38,777 --> 00:13:43,114
OH, WE SHOULD NOT TEAR
AT EACH OTHER SO, PAVEL.

244
00:13:43,239 --> 00:13:46,326
WE SHOULD
MEET AGAIN IN JOY.

245
00:13:46,451 --> 00:13:48,911
TODAY WHEN I FIRST
KNEW IT WAS YOUR SHIP
THAT FOLLOWED US,

246
00:13:49,036 --> 00:13:53,750
I THOUGHT OF YOU
AND WONDERED WHAT
I WOULD FIND.

247
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:57,003
AND I REMEMBERED SO MUCH.

248
00:13:59,339 --> 00:14:01,633
IN SPITE OF THAT UNIFORM,

249
00:14:01,758 --> 00:14:06,262
I STILL SEE THE SAME
PAVEL I USED TO KNOW.

250
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:12,727
ARE YOU HAPPY
IN WHAT YOU DO?

251
00:14:12,851 --> 00:14:14,853
YES.

252
00:14:15,896 --> 00:14:18,608
THEN I ACCEPT
WHAT YOU DO.

253
00:14:18,733 --> 00:14:20,860
YOU EVEN TALK
LIKE THEM.

254
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,950
WHY DID YOU GO AWAY?

255
00:14:28,075 --> 00:14:30,411
IT WAS YOU WHO WENT.

256
00:14:30,537 --> 00:14:32,831
I CAME BACK
TO LOOK FOR YOU.

257
00:14:32,955 --> 00:14:34,999
I LOOKED...

258
00:14:35,667 --> 00:14:37,460
WHERE DID YOU GO?

259
00:14:37,585 --> 00:14:40,171
I STAYED IN THE CITY...

260
00:14:40,296 --> 00:14:41,881
WITH FRIENDS.

261
00:14:43,508 --> 00:14:46,720
YOU NEVER FELT
AS I DID. NEVER.

262
00:14:46,845 --> 00:14:49,013
I<i> DID.</i>

263
00:14:49,138 --> 00:14:51,474
YOU DON'T HAVE IT IN
YOU TO FEEL SO MUCH.

264
00:14:51,599 --> 00:14:54,769
EVEN WHEN WE WERE CLOSE,
YOU WEREN'T WITH ME.

265
00:14:54,894 --> 00:14:58,356
YOU WERE OFF...THINKING
OF SOMETHING ELSE.

266
00:14:58,481 --> 00:15:01,860
THEN WHY DID
YOU STAY AWAY?

267
00:15:01,984 --> 00:15:05,822
BECAUSE YOU
DISAPPROVED OF ME...

268
00:15:05,946 --> 00:15:08,449
JUST AS YOU DO NOW.

269
00:15:10,951 --> 00:15:14,038
OH, PAVEL, YOU HAVE
ALWAYS BEEN LIKE THIS--

270
00:15:14,163 --> 00:15:15,915
SO CORRECT.

271
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:18,585
AND INSIDE, THE
STRUGGLE NOT TO BE.

272
00:15:18,710 --> 00:15:21,921
GIVE IN TO YOURSELF.
YOU WILL BE HAPPIER.

273
00:15:22,046 --> 00:15:24,048
YOU'LL SEE.

274
00:15:28,553 --> 00:15:30,889
GO TO YOUR FRIENDS.

275
00:15:45,486 --> 00:15:46,613
[MUFFLED SHOUTING]

276
00:15:49,574 --> 00:15:52,744
FREE DR. SEVRIN!
FREE DR. SEVRIN!

277
00:15:59,041 --> 00:16:00,418
GET BACK!

278
00:16:00,543 --> 00:16:02,211
Man: BUT WE WANT
TO SEE HIM NOW!

279
00:16:07,258 --> 00:16:07,884
Protesters: HERBERT! HERBERT!
HERBERT! HERBERT!

280
00:16:08,008 --> 00:16:10,553
Chapel: I THOUGHT
ALL THE ANIMALS
WERE KEPT IN CAGES.

281
00:16:10,678 --> 00:16:12,305
Kirk: WHAT'S
GOING ON, BONES?

282
00:16:13,222 --> 00:16:14,348
TROUBLE.

283
00:16:14,474 --> 00:16:15,767
YOUR FRIEND HERE
DIDN'T WANT A CHECKUP.

284
00:16:15,892 --> 00:16:17,477
TURNS OUT
THERE'S A REASON.

285
00:16:17,602 --> 00:16:18,812
I REFUSE TO ACCEPT
YOUR FINDINGS.

286
00:16:18,937 --> 00:16:19,729
YOU DON'T HAVE THE CHOICE.

287
00:16:19,854 --> 00:16:21,773
THEY'RE THE PRODUCT
OF PREJUDICE,
NOT SCIENCE.

288
00:16:21,898 --> 00:16:24,358
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THIS MAN
WAS PLANNING ON DOING

289
00:16:24,484 --> 00:16:27,153
ON A PRIMITIVE PLANET,
BUT ASSUMING ONE DID EXIST,

290
00:16:27,278 --> 00:16:28,571
I CAN TELL YOU
WHAT WOULD HAVE HAPPENED
HAD HE SETTLED THERE--

291
00:16:28,696 --> 00:16:30,615
UNTRUE!

292
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:32,951
THERE WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
ENOUGH OF THOSE PRIMITIVES
LEFT TO BURY THEIR DEAD.

293
00:16:33,075 --> 00:16:34,577
FANTASY,
FANTASY--

294
00:16:34,702 --> 00:16:36,537
I WISH IT WERE.

295
00:16:36,663 --> 00:16:39,833
A NASTY LITTLE
BUG EVOLVED IN THE
LAST FEW YEARS, JIM.

296
00:16:39,958 --> 00:16:42,585
OUR ASEPTIC, STERILIZED
CIVILIZATION HAS PRODUCED IT--

297
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:44,295
<i>SYNTHOCOCCUS NOVAE.</i>
IT'S DEADLY.

298
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,797
WE CAN IMMUNIZE AGAINST IT,

299
00:16:45,922 --> 00:16:48,508
BUT WE HAVEN'T LEARNED
TO LICK ALL THE PROBLEMS YET.

300
00:16:48,633 --> 00:16:51,260
DOES HE HAVE IT?
WHAT ABOUT THE OTHERS?

301
00:16:51,385 --> 00:16:52,219
WELL,
THE OTHERS ARE CLEAR.

302
00:16:52,345 --> 00:16:54,013
HE DOESN'T HAVE IT.
HE'S A CARRIER.

303
00:16:54,138 --> 00:16:55,682
REMEMBER YOUR ANCIENT HISTORY?
TYPHOID MARY?

304
00:16:55,807 --> 00:16:56,850
HE'S IMMUNE TO IT,
AS SHE WAS,

305
00:16:56,975 --> 00:17:00,227
BUT HE CARRIES THE DISEASE
AND SPREADS IT TO OTHERS.

306
00:17:00,353 --> 00:17:01,228
IS THE CREW IN DANGER?

307
00:17:01,354 --> 00:17:03,272
I DON'T KNOW.
THEY ALL HAD

308
00:17:03,397 --> 00:17:05,441
FULL-SPECTRUM
IMMUNIZATIONS BEFORE BOARDING.

309
00:17:05,566 --> 00:17:07,861
NOW, MY GUESS IS
THAT HIS FRIENDS HAVE
HAD THEIR SHOTS, TOO.

310
00:17:07,986 --> 00:17:10,571
BUT A REGULAR PROGRAM
OF BOOSTER SHOTS IS NECESSARY.

311
00:17:10,697 --> 00:17:11,698
I'LL HAVE TO CHECK
EVERYONE ON THE SHIP.

312
00:17:11,823 --> 00:17:13,658
THERE COULD BE SOME SKIPS.
IN THE MEANTIME,

313
00:17:13,783 --> 00:17:16,076
HE SHOULD BE PLACED
IN TOTAL ISOLATION.

314
00:17:16,202 --> 00:17:17,495
THIS IS OUTRAGEOUS.

315
00:17:17,620 --> 00:17:20,540
YOU'RE NOT ISOLATING ME,
YOU'RE IMPRISONING ME.

316
00:17:20,665 --> 00:17:23,584
YOU INVENT THE CRIME,
FIND ME GUILTY,
AND SENTENCE ME.

317
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:25,586
WOULD YOU LIKE TO RUN THE TEST
YOURSELF, DOCTOR?

318
00:17:25,712 --> 00:17:27,296
YOU KNEW YOU WERE A CARRIER
BEFORE YOU CAME ABOARD,

319
00:17:27,421 --> 00:17:28,589
DIDN'T YOU?
NO!

320
00:17:28,715 --> 00:17:29,549
THEN WHY DID YOU FIGHT
THE EXAMINATION?

321
00:17:29,674 --> 00:17:31,759
IT WAS
AN INFRINGEMENT
ON MY RIGHTS!

322
00:17:31,885 --> 00:17:33,845
PUT HIM IN ISOLATION.

323
00:17:44,104 --> 00:17:46,106
BE READY FOR
THE OBJECTIONS, JIM.

324
00:17:46,232 --> 00:17:47,859
THEY ARE A VOCAL LOT.

325
00:17:47,984 --> 00:17:50,778
YES, I'M READY.
KIRK TO SECURITY.

326
00:17:50,904 --> 00:17:53,990
I WANT A GUARD
MAINTAINED ON DR. SEVRIN

327
00:17:54,114 --> 00:17:55,408
UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE.

328
00:17:55,533 --> 00:17:57,744
BONES, HOW LONG
BEFORE WE KNOW

329
00:17:57,869 --> 00:18:00,621
WHETHER THE CREW
HAS BEEN ENDANGERED
BY THIS INFECTION?

330
00:18:00,747 --> 00:18:04,709
IT'LL SHOW IN 24 HOURS.
IT'S A VIRULENT STRAIN.

331
00:18:07,169 --> 00:18:10,089
Woman: YOU DON'T
BELONG WITH THEM.

332
00:18:10,214 --> 00:18:11,090
YOU KNOW WHAT WE WANT.

333
00:18:11,215 --> 00:18:13,467
YOU WANT IT, TOO!

334
00:18:13,593 --> 00:18:15,469
COME, JOIN US!

335
00:18:15,595 --> 00:18:16,930
HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHAT I WANT?

336
00:18:17,055 --> 00:18:19,473
YOU'RE YOUNG.

337
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:21,809
THINK YOUNG,
BROTHER.

338
00:18:21,935 --> 00:18:23,644
YOU MAKE IT TEMPTING.

339
00:18:25,396 --> 00:18:26,606
Kirk:
MR. SULU.

340
00:18:30,276 --> 00:18:31,778
MR. SULU,
EXPLAIN.

341
00:18:31,903 --> 00:18:33,153
UH...

342
00:18:33,279 --> 00:18:35,406
NO EXPLANATION,
SIR.

343
00:18:35,531 --> 00:18:37,951
Kirk: DR. SEVRIN
WILL BE RELEASED

344
00:18:38,076 --> 00:18:40,787
WHEN WE THINK
HE IS MEDICALLY SAFE.

345
00:18:40,912 --> 00:18:42,288
[PLAYING GUITARLIKE MUSIC]

346
00:18:42,413 --> 00:18:44,958
Man: ♪ STIFF MAN
PUTTING MY MIND IN JAIL ♪

347
00:18:45,083 --> 00:18:48,294
♪ AND THE JUDGE BANGED THE GAVEL
AND SAY, "NO BAIL" ♪

348
00:18:48,419 --> 00:18:51,589
♪ GONNA LICK HIS HAND
AND WAG MY TAIL ♪

349
00:18:51,714 --> 00:18:54,508
All: HERBERT! HERBERT!
HERBERT! HERBERT!

350
00:18:54,634 --> 00:18:56,594
HERBERT! HERBERT!
HERBERT! HERBERT!

351
00:18:56,719 --> 00:18:59,013
[INTERCOM WHISTLES]

352
00:18:59,138 --> 00:19:01,474
Scott, on intercom:
ENGINEERING TO BRIDGE.

353
00:19:01,599 --> 00:19:02,558
YES, SCOTTY.
WHAT IS IT?

354
00:19:02,683 --> 00:19:05,103
CAPTAIN, I JUST HAD
TO GIVE ONE OF THOSE

355
00:19:05,227 --> 00:19:07,271
BAREFOOTED WHADDAYACALLEMS
THE BOOT OUT OF HERE.

356
00:19:07,396 --> 00:19:08,898
SHE CAME IN
BOLD AS BRASS,

357
00:19:09,023 --> 00:19:10,108
TRIED TO INCITE MY
CREW TO DISAFFECT.

358
00:19:10,232 --> 00:19:11,943
THANK YOU,
SCOTTY.

359
00:19:12,068 --> 00:19:14,445
MR. SPOCK,
I DON'T SEEM TO BE ABLE

360
00:19:14,570 --> 00:19:15,863
TO COMMUNICATE
WITH THESE PEOPLE.

361
00:19:15,989 --> 00:19:18,825
DO YOU THINK
YOU CAN PERSUADE THEM TO BEHAVE?

362
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:20,451
I SHALL MAKE
AN ATTEMPT, CAPTAIN.

363
00:19:20,576 --> 00:19:21,911
THANK YOU,
MR. SPOCK.

364
00:19:22,036 --> 00:19:22,912
IF IT WEREN'T FOR
THAT AMBASSADOR'S SON,

365
00:19:23,037 --> 00:19:24,455
THEY'D ALL
BE IN THE BRIG.

366
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:26,206
YES, SIR.

367
00:19:26,332 --> 00:19:29,251
Kirk, voice-over:
CAPTAIN'S LOG, STARDATE 5832.5.

368
00:19:29,376 --> 00:19:32,254
THE ARROGANCE OF DR. SEVRIN
AND HIS FOLLOWERS

369
00:19:32,379 --> 00:19:34,674
IS CREATING AN INTOLERABLE
SITUATION ABOARD THE<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

370
00:19:34,799 --> 00:19:37,593
IF IT CONTINUES,
I'LL BE FORCED TO USE CONTROLS

371
00:19:37,718 --> 00:19:39,720
WHICH MIGHT NOT AGREE
WITH STARFLEET'S SUGGESTION

372
00:19:39,846 --> 00:19:43,474
THAT THEY BE HANDLED
WITH EXTREME TOLERANCE.

373
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:46,060
I HAVE NO INFLUENCE
OVER WHAT THEY DO.

374
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:47,436
THEY RESPECT YOU.

375
00:19:47,561 --> 00:19:49,939
THEY WILL LISTEN
TO YOUR REASONING.

376
00:19:50,064 --> 00:19:54,234
FOR THEIR SAKE,
YOU MUST STOP THEM.

377
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:56,236
DR. SEVRIN, I'M
IN A POSITION TO

378
00:19:56,362 --> 00:19:58,156
HELP YOU AND
YOUR GROUP.

379
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,658
I CAN USE THE
RESOURCES OF
THE<i> ENTERPRISE</i>

380
00:20:00,783 --> 00:20:04,162
TO DETERMINE
WHETHER OR NOT
EDEN ACTUALLY EXISTS

381
00:20:04,286 --> 00:20:06,372
AND TO PLOT ITS
EXACT LOCATION.

382
00:20:06,497 --> 00:20:08,415
I CAN PRESENT A
CASE TO FEDERATION

383
00:20:08,541 --> 00:20:10,001
TO ALLOW YOU AND
YOUR GROUP TO

384
00:20:10,126 --> 00:20:12,670
COLONIZE THAT
PLANET.

385
00:20:12,795 --> 00:20:15,131
NEITHER YOU NOR YOUR PEOPLE
ARE, AT PRESENT,

386
00:20:15,255 --> 00:20:17,675
CHARGED WITH A CRIME.

387
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:21,470
HOWEVER...
INCITEMENT TO DISAFFECTION...

388
00:20:21,595 --> 00:20:23,430
<i>IS</i> CRIMINAL.

389
00:20:23,556 --> 00:20:26,809
FEDERATION WILL NEVER
ALLOW THE COLONIZATION
OF A PLANET BY CRIMINALS.

390
00:20:26,934 --> 00:20:29,353
IF THEY PERSIST,
THEY WILL BE SO CHARGED

391
00:20:29,478 --> 00:20:31,814
AND FOREVER BARRED
FROM EDEN.

392
00:20:31,939 --> 00:20:33,399
AS I HAVE BEEN BARRED?

393
00:20:33,524 --> 00:20:36,777
THEN YOU KNEW
YOU WERE A CARRIER?

394
00:20:36,903 --> 00:20:38,654
OF COURSE I KNEW!

395
00:20:40,656 --> 00:20:43,617
YOU'VE RESEARCHED
MY LIFE.

396
00:20:43,743 --> 00:20:46,204
YOU'VE READ THE ORDERS
RESTRICTING ME TO TRAVEL

397
00:20:46,328 --> 00:20:48,372
ONLY IN AREAS OF
ADVANCED TECHNOLOGY

398
00:20:48,497 --> 00:20:50,249
BECAUSE OF WHAT
MY BODY CARRIES.

399
00:20:50,374 --> 00:20:51,458
WHAT I FAIL TO UNDERSTAND

400
00:20:51,584 --> 00:20:53,252
IS WHY YOU DISOBEY
THOSE ORDERS.

401
00:20:53,377 --> 00:20:57,965
BECAUSE THIS
IS POISON TO ME!

402
00:20:59,926 --> 00:21:02,803
THIS...

403
00:21:02,929 --> 00:21:04,889
<i>STUFF</i> YOU BREATHE,

404
00:21:05,014 --> 00:21:08,684
THIS STUFF YOU LIVE IN...

405
00:21:08,809 --> 00:21:11,062
SHIELDS OF
ARTIFICIAL ATMOSPHERE

406
00:21:11,187 --> 00:21:15,816
THAT WE HAVE LAYERED
ABOUT EVERY PLANET...

407
00:21:15,942 --> 00:21:18,652
THE PROGRAMS
IN THOSE COMPUTERS

408
00:21:18,778 --> 00:21:22,489
THAT RUN YOUR SHIP
AND YOUR LIVES FOR YOU...

409
00:21:22,615 --> 00:21:26,619
THEY BRED WHAT
MY BODY CARRIES.

410
00:21:27,995 --> 00:21:31,415
THAT'S WHAT YOUR
SCIENCE HAVE DONE TO ME.

411
00:21:33,251 --> 00:21:35,419
YOU'VE INFECTED ME!

412
00:21:40,507 --> 00:21:43,343
ONLY THE PRIMITIVES
CAN CLEANSE ME.

413
00:21:43,469 --> 00:21:46,597
I CANNOT PURGE MYSELF
UNTIL I AM AMONG THEM.

414
00:21:46,722 --> 00:21:49,600
ONLY THEIR WAY OF LIVING
IS RIGHT.

415
00:21:49,725 --> 00:21:51,811
I MUST GO TO THEM.

416
00:21:51,936 --> 00:21:55,606
YOUR VERY PRESENCE WILL DESTROY
THE PEOPLE YOU SEEK.

417
00:21:55,731 --> 00:21:57,150
SURELY YOU KNOW THAT.

418
00:21:57,275 --> 00:22:01,237
I SHALL GO TO THEM
AND BE ONE WITH THEM.

419
00:22:01,361 --> 00:22:03,864
AND TOGETHER,
WE SHALL BUILD A WORLD

420
00:22:03,990 --> 00:22:06,826
SUCH AS THIS GALAXY
HAS NEVER SEEN.

421
00:22:06,951 --> 00:22:10,913
A WORLD...
A LIFE...

422
00:22:11,038 --> 00:22:13,707
A LIFE.

423
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:24,177
SO NOW YOU'RE GOING
TO TRY TO PERSUADE ME

424
00:22:24,302 --> 00:22:26,344
THAT YOUR TECHNOLOGIES
WILL FIND A CURE FOR ME

425
00:22:26,470 --> 00:22:28,806
AND THEN I'LL
BE FREE TO GO.

426
00:22:28,931 --> 00:22:30,099
YES, DOCTOR.

427
00:22:30,224 --> 00:22:32,601
AND FOR THAT REASON,

428
00:22:32,726 --> 00:22:34,394
I SHOULD PERSUADE
MY FRIENDS TO BEHAVE

429
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:36,314
SO THAT THEY, TOO,
WILL BE ALLOWED?

430
00:22:36,438 --> 00:22:37,690
YES, DOCTOR.

431
00:22:40,567 --> 00:22:42,778
ALL RIGHT,
YOU SEND THEM IN.

432
00:22:42,903 --> 00:22:44,697
I'LL TALK TO THEM.

433
00:22:53,622 --> 00:22:55,166
DR. SEVRIN...

434
00:22:55,291 --> 00:22:56,792
IS INSANE.

435
00:22:56,917 --> 00:22:59,212
I'VE NOT CONSULTED
DR. McCOY,

436
00:22:59,337 --> 00:23:01,755
BUT I HAVE
NO DOUBT OF IT.

437
00:23:01,881 --> 00:23:04,424
I'LL HAVE BONES
CHECK HIM OUT.

438
00:23:04,550 --> 00:23:06,468
SPOCK, I'M SORRY.

439
00:23:06,593 --> 00:23:08,346
YOU HAD GREAT
RESPECT FOR HIM.

440
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,931
BUT IT DOES
EXPLAIN SOME OF
WHAT THEY'VE DONE.

441
00:23:11,057 --> 00:23:15,393
HIS CONDITION DOES NOT
AFFECT MY INTEREST
IN THE MOVEMENT.

442
00:23:15,519 --> 00:23:18,605
THERE IS NO INSANITY
IN WHAT THEY SEEK.

443
00:23:19,565 --> 00:23:20,398
I MADE A PROMISE,

444
00:23:20,524 --> 00:23:23,569
WHICH I SHOULD
LIKE TO KEEP.

445
00:23:23,694 --> 00:23:27,405
WITH YOUR PERMISSION,
I MUST LOCATE EDEN.

446
00:23:27,531 --> 00:23:30,576
I SHALL WORK
IN MY QUARTERS.

447
00:23:30,701 --> 00:23:32,578
MAY I HAVE THE
ASSISTANCE OF MR. CHEKOV

448
00:23:32,703 --> 00:23:34,496
IN AUXILIARY CONTROL?

449
00:23:36,123 --> 00:23:37,750
CERTAINLY.

450
00:23:38,709 --> 00:23:40,836
MR. CHEKOV,
ASSIST MR. SPOCK.

451
00:23:41,712 --> 00:23:43,172
BRIDGE TO SICK BAY.

452
00:23:43,297 --> 00:23:43,839
On intercom:
McCOY HERE.

453
00:23:43,964 --> 00:23:45,007
BONES.

454
00:23:45,132 --> 00:23:46,300
YES, CAPTAIN?

455
00:23:46,424 --> 00:23:48,677
I'D LIKE
TO TALK TO YOU.

456
00:23:49,845 --> 00:23:52,098
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG,
STARDATE 5832.6.

457
00:23:52,223 --> 00:23:53,431
I HAVE ASKED DR. McCOY

458
00:23:53,557 --> 00:23:55,517
TO CHECK STARFLEET
MEDICAL RECORDS

459
00:23:55,642 --> 00:23:58,562
TO VERIFY MR. SPOCK'S SUSPICION
THAT DR. SEVRIN IS INSANE.

460
00:23:58,687 --> 00:24:01,481
