00:25:49,923 --> 00:25:52,550
I HAVE BEEN LOOKING
FOR YOU, PAVEL.

490
00:25:55,929 --> 00:25:58,015
WHAT ROOM IS THIS?

491
00:25:58,140 --> 00:26:00,309
AUXILIARY CONTROL.

492
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:03,229
WHAT'S IT FOR?

493
00:26:03,354 --> 00:26:05,231
SHOULD THE MAIN
CONTROL ROOM BREAK DOWN

494
00:26:05,356 --> 00:26:06,857
OR SUFFER DAMAGE,

495
00:26:06,982 --> 00:26:09,985
WE CAN NAVIGATE
THE SHIP FROM HERE.

496
00:26:13,780 --> 00:26:15,699
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

497
00:26:16,158 --> 00:26:18,244
TO APOLOGIZE.

498
00:26:18,369 --> 00:26:20,204
I SHOULD NOT
HAVE TEASED YOU.

499
00:26:20,329 --> 00:26:22,373
IT WAS CRUEL.

500
00:26:22,498 --> 00:26:23,790
IT DOES NOT MATTER.

501
00:26:23,916 --> 00:26:25,501
OH, BUT IT DOES.

502
00:26:25,625 --> 00:26:29,587
