PROBLEMS OF NAVIGATION,

524
00:27:50,336 --> 00:27:52,796
OF CONTROL...

525
00:27:52,921 --> 00:27:55,257
OF LIFE...SUPPORT.

526
00:27:55,382 --> 00:27:58,177
