ANY SPECIAL WAYS
TO SWING THEM?

558
00:29:36,983 --> 00:29:38,318
JUST BE FRIENDLY.

559
00:29:38,444 --> 00:29:41,530
YOU KNOW HOW
TO BE FRIENDLY.

560
00:29:43,741 --> 00:29:45,701
