♪ YEA ♪

698
00:38:57,877 --> 00:39:00,964
THEY ARE WITHIN
SENSOR RANGE OF EDEN

699
00:39:01,089 --> 00:39:03,424
AND CONTINUING
TO APPROACH.

700
00:39:03,549 --> 00:39:06,594
WHATEVER THEY'RE GONNA DO,
THEY'RE GONNA DO NOW.

701
00:39:06,719 --> 00:39:08,221
WE HAVE NO CHOICE.

702
00:39:08,346 --> 00:39:09,555
MR. SPOCK, MR. SCOTT.

703
00:39:12,142 --> 00:39:13,268
Adam:
WHEN WILL YOU USE THAT?

704
00:39:13,392 --> 00:39:15,561
AT THE PROPER TIME.

705
00:39:15,687 --> 00:39:17,438
LET ME KNOW
WHEN WE'RE IN ORBIT.

706
00:39:17,563 --> 00:39:18,815
APPROACHING
RIGHT ON THE DOT,

707
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:20,025
JUST AS THEY PLOTTED
IT, BROTHER SEVRIN.

708
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:21,609
WHAT WILL THAT
DO TO THEM?

709
00:39:21,734 --> 00:39:23,111
WHAT IS IT?

710
00:39:23,236 --> 00:39:25,613
WELL, I'M USING SOUND
AGAINST THEM--

711
00:39:25,738 --> 00:39:27,199
BEYOND THE ULTRASONIC.

712
00:39:27,324 --> 00:39:29,117
IT WILL STUN THEM
AND ALLOW US TIME TO LEAVE.

713
00:39:29,242 --> 00:39:31,036
WE'LL GO IN ONE
OF THEIR SHUTTLECRAFT.

714
00:39:31,161 --> 00:39:32,996
SOUND PITCHED
THAT HIGH
DOESN'T STUN--

715
00:39:33,121 --> 00:39:35,165
IT DESTROYS.

716
00:39:35,290 --> 00:39:37,542
I REMEMBER
WHEN WE READ IN
THE TEXT THAT IT--

717
00:39:37,667 --> 00:39:40,086
I'VE GONE BEYOND
THOSE TEXTS, IRINA.

718
00:39:40,212 --> 00:39:43,381
IT'S CORRECT FOR YOU
TO BE CONCERNED...

719
00:39:43,506 --> 00:39:45,133
BUT BE ASSURED ALSO.

720
00:39:47,302 --> 00:39:48,553
WE ARE IN ORBIT
OVER EDEN,

721
00:39:48,678 --> 00:39:50,388
BROTHER SEVRIN.

722
00:39:51,514 --> 00:39:53,599
IT DOES DESTROY.

723
00:39:55,101 --> 00:39:58,104
WE CANNOT ALLOW THEM
TO COME AFTER US.

724
00:39:58,230 --> 00:39:59,939
IT WILL NOT
REACH US IN HERE.

725
00:40:00,065 --> 00:40:01,900
I CAN CONTROL IT ALL.

726
00:40:02,025 --> 00:40:04,777
I HAVE ADJUSTED IT SO THAT
IT WILL SUSPEND ITS EFFECTS

727
00:40:04,903 --> 00:40:07,197
AFTER A FEW MOMENTS
AND ALLOW US TIME TO ESCAPE.

728
00:40:07,322 --> 00:40:09,115
THEN, AFTER WE'VE GONE,

729
00:40:09,241 --> 00:40:13,161
IT WILL AUTOMATICALLY
REACTIVATE.

730
00:40:13,286 --> 00:40:15,330
REJOICE, BRETHREN.

731
00:40:15,454 --> 00:40:18,833
SOON WE SHALL STEP
TOGETHER INTO EDEN.

732
00:40:19,834 --> 00:40:21,627
[PHASER FIRING]

733
00:40:42,357 --> 00:40:43,691
[SILENCE]

734
00:40:44,567 --> 00:40:45,610
SPOCK.

735
00:40:51,866 --> 00:40:54,160
IT'S ALL RIGHT, SPOCK.
IT STOPPED.

736
00:40:54,286 --> 00:40:56,288
NO, CAPTAIN,
IT HASN'T STOPPED.

737
00:40:56,413 --> 00:40:58,081
IT HAS GONE BEYOND--

738
00:40:59,498 --> 00:41:01,376
CAPTAIN,
THEY'RE USING--

739
00:41:10,468 --> 00:41:12,845
Adam: ♪ STEPPIN'
INTO EDEN ♪

740
00:41:12,971 --> 00:41:14,764
Adam, women:
♪ YEA, BROTHER ♪

741
00:41:14,889 --> 00:41:16,891
♪ STEPPIN'
INTO EDEN ♪

742
00:41:17,016 --> 00:41:18,684
♪ YEA, BROTHER ♪

743
00:41:18,810 --> 00:41:22,730
♪ NO MORE TROUBLE
IN MY BODY OR MY MIND ♪

744
00:41:22,855 --> 00:41:26,734
♪ GONNA LIVE LIKE A KING
ON WHATEVER I FIND ♪

745
00:41:26,859 --> 00:41:31,072
♪ EAT ALL THE FRUIT
AND THROW AWAY THE RIND ♪

746
00:41:31,197 --> 00:41:35,618
♪ YEA, BROTHER ♪

747
00:41:36,869 --> 00:41:38,579
NOW WE MAY LEAVE.

748
00:41:47,464 --> 00:41:48,923
AGH.

749
00:41:49,048 --> 00:41:51,426
CAPTAIN, GO.

750
00:41:51,550 --> 00:41:53,928
YOU MUST...
DESTROY THE--

751
00:41:54,053 --> 00:41:55,847
WHAT IS IT?

752
00:41:55,972 --> 00:41:57,807
ULTRASONICS.

753
00:41:57,932 --> 00:41:59,684
THE PANEL.

754
00:42:22,081 --> 00:42:23,875
KIRK TO ENGINEERING.

755
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:25,626
BRIDGE.

756
00:42:27,003 --> 00:42:28,546
HANGAR DECK.

757
00:42:32,425 --> 00:42:34,511
KIRK TO TRANSPORTER ROOM.

758
00:42:36,804 --> 00:42:38,223
KIRK TO BRIDGE.

759
00:42:38,348 --> 00:42:40,058
DO YOU READ ME?
COME IN.

760
00:42:40,183 --> 00:42:41,642
On intercom:
SULU HERE, CAPTAIN.

761
00:42:41,767 --> 00:42:44,687
WHAT HAPPENED TO US?
I HEARD A WHISTLE,
AND THEN--

762
00:42:44,812 --> 00:42:46,814
NEVER MIND.
DO WE HAVE CONTROL OF THE SHIP?

763
00:42:46,939 --> 00:42:48,024
Chekov,
on intercom:
NO, SIR.

764
00:42:48,149 --> 00:42:49,650
CONTROL
IS IN AUXILIARY.

765
00:42:49,775 --> 00:42:51,652
CAN WE BREAK OUT OF
ORBIT IF WE HAVE TO?

766
00:42:51,777 --> 00:42:52,653
I THINK SO, SIR.

767
00:42:52,778 --> 00:42:54,447
Man, on intercom:
HANGAR DECK
TO CAPTAIN.

768
00:42:54,572 --> 00:42:56,032
KIRK HERE.

769
00:42:56,157 --> 00:42:57,825
SIR, ONE OF THE
SHUTTLECRAFTS
HAS BEEN TAKEN.

770
00:42:57,950 --> 00:42:59,452
WE WERE ALL
KNOCKED OUT.

771
00:42:59,577 --> 00:43:01,037
STAND BY.
DO YOU READ ANY ROMULANS?

772
00:43:01,162 --> 00:43:02,621
NEGATIVE, CAPTAIN.

773
00:43:02,747 --> 00:43:05,208
HOWEVER, I AM PICKING UP
THE SHUTTLECRAFT.

774
00:43:05,333 --> 00:43:06,251
WHERE?

775
00:43:06,376 --> 00:43:07,544
IT HAS LANDED.

776
00:43:07,668 --> 00:43:09,087
EXCEPT FOR THOSE
ABOARD THE CRAFT,

777
00:43:09,212 --> 00:43:10,796
I READ NO LIFE AT ALL,

778
00:43:10,922 --> 00:43:12,673
NEITHER HUMANOID
NOR ANIMAL.

779
00:43:15,510 --> 00:43:17,929
AUXILIARY CONTROL
TO DR. McCOY.

780
00:43:18,054 --> 00:43:19,556
BONES, ARE
YOU ALL RIGHT?

781
00:43:19,680 --> 00:43:20,639
McCoy, on intercom:
YES, JIM.

782
00:43:20,765 --> 00:43:23,642
STAND BY, TRANSPORTER ROOM.
FULL MEDICAL GEAR.

783
00:43:23,768 --> 00:43:25,978
Chekov, on intercom:
BRIDGE TO CAPTAIN KIRK.

784
00:43:26,104 --> 00:43:28,022
DO YOU WISH TO OPEN
COMMUNICATIONS, SIR?

785
00:43:28,147 --> 00:43:31,484
NO. NO.
THEY TRIED TO DESTROY US.

786
00:43:31,609 --> 00:43:33,652
LET THEM THINK
THEY SUCCEEDED.

787
00:43:33,778 --> 00:43:35,113
I WANT THE COORDINATES
ZEROED IN

788
00:43:35,238 --> 00:43:37,656
SO THAT WHEN WE BEAM DOWN,
WE WON'T BE VISIBLE TO THEM.

789
00:43:37,782 --> 00:43:39,492
SCOTTY, YOU
HAVE THE CON.

790
00:43:39,617 --> 00:43:43,037
IF ANY ROMULANS APPEAR,
TRY TO MAKE THEM UNDERSTAND.

791
00:43:43,162 --> 00:43:46,291
I DO NOT WANT
TO PROVOKE COMBAT.

792
00:43:46,416 --> 00:43:47,584
MR. SPOCK...

793
00:43:47,708 --> 00:43:51,296
MR. CHEKOV, JOIN US
IN THE TRANSPORTER ROOM.

794
00:44:09,481 --> 00:44:11,149
[TRICORDER HUMMING]

795
00:44:16,446 --> 00:44:18,531
THE LEGENDS
WERE TRUE, CAPTAIN.

796
00:44:18,656 --> 00:44:21,367
A FANTASTICALLY
BEAUTIFUL PLANET.

797
00:44:21,493 --> 00:44:22,535
Chekov: EDEN.

798
00:44:22,660 --> 00:44:25,746
IS THIS WHAT THEY
BELIEVED THEY'D FIND?

799
00:44:25,871 --> 00:44:27,582
THEN I CAN UNDERSTAND.

800
00:44:28,791 --> 00:44:29,875
[TRICORDER STOPS HUMMING]

801
00:44:30,001 --> 00:44:31,085
[COMMUNICATOR OPENS]

802
00:44:31,210 --> 00:44:32,128
SPREAD OUT.

803
00:44:32,253 --> 00:44:34,506
APPROACH WITH CAUTION.

804
00:44:38,009 --> 00:44:39,302
DR. SEVRIN.

805
00:44:39,427 --> 00:44:40,928
AAH!

806
00:44:45,433 --> 00:44:46,351
WHAT IS IT?

807
00:44:46,476 --> 00:44:49,020
THE FLOWER, SIR.
I TOUCHED IT.

808
00:44:49,145 --> 00:44:50,563
IT'S LIKE FIRE.

809
00:44:53,024 --> 00:44:54,609
IT'S BURNED.

810
00:44:59,155 --> 00:45:02,367
ALL THIS PLANT LIFE
IS FULL OF ACID.

811
00:45:05,495 --> 00:45:07,372
EVEN THE GRASS, JIM.

812
00:45:09,290 --> 00:45:10,625
WILL OUR CLOTHING
PROTECT US?

813
00:45:10,749 --> 00:45:12,669
IT SHOULD,
FOR A WHILE.

814
00:45:12,793 --> 00:45:14,379
Spock:
CAPTAIN.

815
00:45:32,771 --> 00:45:34,148
BONES?

816
00:45:36,775 --> 00:45:38,069
POISON.

817
00:45:38,194 --> 00:45:39,696
THE FRUIT IS DEADLY.

818
00:45:40,112 --> 00:45:42,073
HIS NAME WAS ADAM.

819
00:45:48,413 --> 00:45:50,248
Kirk:
THERE'S THE SHUTTLECRAFT.

820
00:46:13,730 --> 00:46:15,064
[IRINA GASPING]

821
00:46:15,189 --> 00:46:16,815
HERE.
WE'LL HELP YOU.

822
00:46:16,941 --> 00:46:18,817
OH! AH!

823
00:46:28,202 --> 00:46:30,829
DR. SEVRIN--
BONES!

824
00:46:33,291 --> 00:46:35,792
McCoy: HE SHOULD BE
BEAMED ABOARD, JIM.

825
00:46:35,918 --> 00:46:37,920
HE NEEDS MORE
THAN I CAN DO FOR HIM HERE.

826
00:46:38,045 --> 00:46:39,338
SPOCK
TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

827
00:46:39,464 --> 00:46:40,590
Scott, on communicator:
<i>ENTERPRISE</i> HERE.

828
00:46:40,715 --> 00:46:42,383
STAND BY TO BEAM ABOARD
INJURED PARTIES.

829
00:46:42,508 --> 00:46:44,469
A MEDICAL TEAM
TO THE TRANSPORTER ROOM.

830
00:46:44,594 --> 00:46:46,971
NO...NO,
WE'RE NOT LEAVING.

831
00:46:47,096 --> 00:46:49,307
WE CAN HELP YOU
ABOARD THE SHIP.

832
00:46:49,432 --> 00:46:50,807
WE'RE NOT
LEAVING EDEN.

833
00:46:50,933 --> 00:46:52,435
NONE OF US.

834
00:46:52,560 --> 00:46:54,270
BE SENSIBLE, DOCTOR.

835
00:46:54,395 --> 00:46:56,564
WE'RE NOT LEAVING.

836
00:46:58,107 --> 00:47:00,943
McCoy: COME BACK
HERE, YOU FOOL!

837
00:47:05,531 --> 00:47:06,741
Kirk: SEVRIN, DON'T!

838
00:47:06,865 --> 00:47:07,408
YOU'LL KILL YOURSELF!

839
00:47:07,533 --> 00:47:09,285
McCoy:
DON'T BITE INTO THAT!

840
00:47:09,410 --> 00:47:10,703
Kirk: STOP!

841
00:47:12,913 --> 00:47:15,583
IT WAS
SO BEAUTIFUL!

842
00:47:36,521 --> 00:47:38,439
Lieutenant Palmer: I HAVE
STARBASE NOW, CAPTAIN.

843
00:47:38,564 --> 00:47:40,899
Kirk: ALERT THEM
THAT WE HAVE THE FOUR

844
00:47:41,025 --> 00:47:42,943
AND WE'RE READY
TO BEAM THEM DOWN,

845
00:47:43,068 --> 00:47:44,362
AND MARK THE
INCIDENT CLOSED.

846
00:47:44,487 --> 00:47:45,822
AYE, SIR.

847
00:47:46,823 --> 00:47:49,701
BRIDGE TO TRANSPORTER.
SCOTTY, ARE THEY THERE?

848
00:47:49,826 --> 00:47:50,284
Scott, on intercom:
THREE OF THEM, SIR.

849
00:47:50,409 --> 00:47:51,952
EXPECTING A
FOURTH ANY MINUTE.

850
00:47:52,077 --> 00:47:53,412
STAND BY.

851
00:47:54,163 --> 00:47:56,415
MR. CHEKOV...

852
00:47:56,541 --> 00:47:58,793
DO YOU WISH TO ATTEND?

853
00:47:58,917 --> 00:48:01,337
CAPTAIN, I WISH
FIRST TO APOLOGIZE

854
00:48:01,462 --> 00:48:03,880
FOR MY CONDUCT
DURING THIS TIME.

855
00:48:04,006 --> 00:48:07,092
I DID NOT MAINTAIN MYSELF
UNDER PROPER DISCIPLINE.

856
00:48:07,218 --> 00:48:10,262
I ENDANGERED THE SHIP
AND ITS PERSONNEL BY MY CONDUCT.

857
00:48:10,388 --> 00:48:13,641
I RESPECTFULLY SUBMIT MYSELF
FOR DISCIPLINARY ACTION.

858
00:48:13,766 --> 00:48:15,309
THANK YOU,
MR. CHEKOV.

859
00:48:15,434 --> 00:48:18,646
YOU DID WHAT
YOU HAD TO DO,

860
00:48:18,771 --> 00:48:20,648
AS DID WE ALL.

861
00:48:20,773 --> 00:48:22,899
EVEN YOUR FRIENDS.

862
00:48:23,776 --> 00:48:25,486
YOU MAY GO.

863
00:48:26,404 --> 00:48:27,572
THANK YOU, SIR.

864
00:48:36,581 --> 00:48:39,458
I WAS COMING
TO SAY GOODBYE.

865
00:48:39,584 --> 00:48:43,713
AND I WAS COMING
TO SAY GOODBYE TO YOU.

866
00:48:50,177 --> 00:48:53,514
BE INCORRECT...
OCCASIONALLY.

867
00:48:53,639 --> 00:48:55,600
AND YOU BE CORRECT.

868
00:48:57,226 --> 00:48:58,935
OCCASIONALLY.

869
00:48:59,270 --> 00:49:01,355
Spock:
MISS GALLIULIN.

870
00:49:03,649 --> 00:49:09,280
IT IS MY SINCERE WISH
THAT YOU DO NOT GIVE UP
YOUR SEARCH FOR EDEN.

871
00:49:09,405 --> 00:49:12,825
I HAVE NO DOUBT
BUT THAT YOU WILL
FIND IT--

872
00:49:12,949 --> 00:49:15,077
OR MAKE IT
YOURSELVES.

873
00:49:15,202 --> 00:49:16,704
THANK YOU.

874
00:49:36,390 --> 00:49:38,392
WE...REACH,
MR. SPOCK.
